Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm planning to change\Nmyself in the new town.}Em muốn đến một thành phố mới,\Nlàm lại từ đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.94,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{Don't worry. Rhint is here with me.}Đừng lo. Hơn nữa, có Rhint bên em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.19,Main,split,0,0,0,,{That guy that was just here?}Cái anh vừa ở đây à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.31,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Something on your mind?}Anh khó chịu sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{To tell the truth, I already have 3 kids.}Thật ra, em đã có ba đứa con.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm just kidding. It was a joke!}Em đùa đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{Rhint is just my boyfriend.}Rhint chỉ là bạn trai của em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{How are you doing?}Anh thì sao rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{Have you gotten married yet?}Anh lấy vợ chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{I live and wander with a group of weirdos.}Anh vẫn sống và đi đây đi đó\Nvới một lũ lập dị.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{And on top of it, I'm a bounty hunter now.}Anh chỉ là gã săn tiền thưởng hèn mọn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{Do you remember?}Nhìn quen không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Where's Jet?}{\i0}{\i1}Jet ở đâu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{Doing personal stuff.}Đi công chuyện rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:52.02,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're his partner, right?}{\i0}Anh là cộng sự của anh ấy, phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:52.68,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I've got news on a bounty.}{\i0}{\i1}Có tin về một khoản tiền thưởng.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{publicly broadcast yet.}{\i0}{\i1}Vẫn chưa được công bố.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:05.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Rhint Celonius.}{\i0}{\i1}Rhint Celonius,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:08.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{A thug in the port of Marvis.}{\i0}{\i1}một tên du côn ở cảng Marvis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{financial broker Law Rentzuo.}{\i0}{\i1}Tối qua, một gã môi giới tài chính{\i0}\N{\i1}tên Law Rentzuo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This guy was another tough guy,}{\i0}{\i1}Ừ thì gã cũng không tốt lành gì nhưng...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:15.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but he was killed!}{\i0}{\i1}Gã đã bị giết.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{And so?}Thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Rhint is Alisa's gigolo.}{\i0}{\i1}Rhint là người yêu của Alisa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I thought I'd warn you guys.}{\i0}{\i1}Tôi nghĩ tôi nên cho anh biết.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:29.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{And how much is the bounty?}Tiền thưởng là bao nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{Back then, when I got home from work,}Hồi đó, mỗi khi anh đi làm về,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{you always waited for me.}em luôn đợi anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{That was all I needed.}Hồi đó anh chỉ cần có thế thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{But that day...}Nhưng hôm đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:58.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{When I came home, only that watch was left}Khi anh về nhà, chỉ còn lại cái đồng hồ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:03.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{and a small note with one word: "farewell".}với dòng chữ "Vĩnh biệt".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{For some reason, I didn't feel sad.}Kỳ lạ thay, anh đã không thấy buồn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:12.83,Main,split,0,0,0,,{It just...}Vì nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.95,Main,split,0,0,0,,{lacked reality.}có vẻ không thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:22.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{And I gradually felt something\Ninside me go numb.}Rồi anh bắt đầu cảm thấy bên trong anh\Ncó gì đó tê liệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{After 6 months, I made a bet with myself.}Sáu tháng sau, anh tự nhủ với bản thân,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{That I would leave this\Nplanet if you didn't return}nếu cái đồng hồ này dừng lại\Ntrước khi em trở về,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{by the time this clock stopped.}anh sẽ rời khỏi hành tinh này.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{I didn't come here to blame you.}Anh không đến đây để trách em.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:44.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{I just wanted to know}Anh chỉ muốn biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:48.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{why you disappeared back then.}Anh muốn biết tại sao\Nngày đó em bỏ anh mà đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:53.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{You seem to think that}Cứ như thể đối với anh,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:58.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{time on Ganymede had stopped.}thời gian ở Ganymede ngừng trôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:03.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{That's a story from long ago.}Anh nhắc lại chuyện quá xa xưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{I've... forgotten it.}Em đã quên mất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:14.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{I don't need time that stands still.}Thời gian đứng yên thì em không cần tới.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Farewell, Jet...}Vĩnh biệt Jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:25.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{A bounty hunter? Then can he be...?}Kẻ săn tiền thưởng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{A bounty hunter? Then can he be...?}Có thể nào hắn...
Comment: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:26.26,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{A bounty hunter? Then can he be...?}Kẻ săn tiền thưởng à? Có thể nào hắn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:28.94,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Rhint...}Rhint...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.49,Main,split,0,0,0,,{He's after me!}Hắn săn đuổi anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{I have a bounty on my head...}Chết tiệt, hẳn là anh đã bị truy nã.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:37.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's all over!}Tất cả kết thúc rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's not your fault.}Không phải lỗi của anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's because I borrowed\Nmoney from a guy like him,}Là tại em đã vay tiền của một gã như hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{and you protected me.}Anh đã bảo vệ em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{I can't be saved if I get caught.}Nếu anh bị bắt, mọi chuyện sẽ kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:54.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{I...}Anh đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{killed a guy...}giết người.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Let's get out of here. [original: "outta"]}Ta bỏ trốn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{Let's get out of here, just the two of us!}Ta sẽ bỏ trốn, chỉ hai chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:39.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{This must be because I have good karma.}Hẳn là do mình ăn ở thiện lành.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, but it's business.}Không thù oán cá nhân gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{Steer for me, please!}Giữ bánh lái!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey? What's wrong?!}{\i0}{\i1}Này, sao thế?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:42.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm after a bounty worth 1.8 million.}Tôi theo đuổi một mục tiêu\Ntrị giá 1,8 triệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:43.41,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What?!}{\i0}Sao cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.73,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Here, I'll send it to you.}{\i0}Đang gửi thông tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{He's a bounty? [9 frames]}Hắn bị truy nã ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.85,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yeah, a secret bit of info from Donelly.}{\i0}Ừ, thông tin hành lang từ Donelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:52.80,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He apparently killed a loan shark.}{\i0}Hắn đã giết một tên cho vay nặng lãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{Dammit!}Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:04.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'll do this. You can go back.}{\i0}{\i1}Để tôi lo. Cậu về đi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{You're not gonna let him go, are ya?}Anh sẽ không để hắn thoát chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:11.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This is the land where I was a cop.}{\i0}{\i1}Tôi từng làm cảnh sát ở đây.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:15.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm the Black Dog.\NOnce I bite, I never let go.}Tôi là Chó Mực.\NMột khi đã cắn, tôi không bao giờ nhả.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:21.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{I have no regrets about her, but I'll\Nsettle this score on my home turf.}{\i1}Tôi không lưu luyến gì cô ấy nữa.{\i0}\N{\i1}Tôi sẽ kết thúc chuyện đã xảy ra ở đây.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{Sense of justice and duty, huh...}Đúng là\Nmột câu chuyện buồn thương chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:32.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Can you hear me...?}{\i0}{\i1}Nghe tôi nói không?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Stop the boat, now!}{\i0}{\i1}Dừng tàu ngay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{Jet?}Jet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:45.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{Stay away!}Lùi lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{Please, let us go!}Xin anh, hãy để anh ấy đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:57.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{There are other bounties to find!}Vẫn còn nhiều gã cho anh truy nã mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{Even if I let you go,}Dù anh để hắn đi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{someone will come for you someday.}ngày nào đó cũng sẽ có kẻ bắt hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:06.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{If you run, you will become an accomplice.}Nếu em bỏ trốn với hắn, em là đồng phạm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:06.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{Stay away!}Lùi lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{You still have time.}Vẫn chưa muộn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about me anymore!}Để em yên!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{You were like this back then, too...}Anh luôn như thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{You decided everything.}Anh quyết định mọi thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{And you were always right...}Và anh luôn đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{When I was with you,\NI never had to do anything.}Khi ở bên anh,\Nem chưa bao giờ phải làm gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:44.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{All I had to do was hang on to your arm\Nlike a child, with no cares in the world.}Tất cả những gì em phải làm\Nlà giữ chặt tay anh như đứa trẻ bất lực.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{I wanted to decide how to\Nlive my life by myself.}Em muốn được quyết định\Ncuộc sống của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:55.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{Even if that was a mistake.}cả khi em phạm phải sai lầm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:16.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Let go! I don't wanna go to prison! Let go!}Bỏ ra! Tôi không muốn đi tù. Bỏ ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Help! Help me, please!}Cứu anh! Làm ơn cứu anh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{Be strong}Đàn ông lên,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:31.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{and protect her.}và bảo vệ cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:49.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{Self-defense seems to\Nbe how they see it.}Có vẻ họ coi đó là tự vệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{What are you going to do now?}Giờ em sẽ làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:58.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{I won't be going anywhere anymore.}Em sẽ không đi đâu cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:02.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{I will wait in my store... for Rhint.}Em sẽ ở lại quán bar đợi Rhint.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:05.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{It won't take long}Sẽ không lâu đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:09.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{because time is flowing along.}vì thời gian không còn đứng yên nữa.
Comment: 1,0:22:31.60,0:22:34.06,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,{\an8}HẸN GẶP LẠI, CAO BỒI VŨ TRỤ...
